10101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>libevent</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">由于</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">memchache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">需要依赖</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">libevent</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">，因此在执行第三步之前，先安装好</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">libevent</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">将</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">libevent</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">进行解压缩：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#tar -zxvf libevent-release-2.1.6-beta.tar.gz</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">进入软件包：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"># cd ./libevent-release-2.1.6-beta</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">运行</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">autogen.sh</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">（自动生成，生成需要的</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">configure</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">）</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#./autogen.sh</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">执行安装：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#./configure --prefix=/usr/local/libevent</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#make &amp;&amp; make install</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">最后看到的界面：</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>③安装</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>memcached</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在安装完成</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">libevent</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">之后需要回到软件包的存放目录：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#cd ..</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">解压软件包：</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">进入压缩包解压目录：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"># cd ./memcached-1.4.31</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">运行</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">autogen.sh</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">生成</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">configure</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#./autogen.sh</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">安装：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#./configure --prefix=/usr/local/memcache --with-libevent=/usr/local/libevent</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#make &amp;&amp; make install</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">最后看到的界面：</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>④目录结构</strong></span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Bin</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">目录：二进制文件的存放目录；</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"52\" width=\"689\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>⑤启动</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><