:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>，</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>65535</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>是</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>16</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>位二进制最大数。</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">-u</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">：以具体的身份执行</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">memchache</span></span></p><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>2、安装memcache扩展</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>①安装</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">解压：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>先回到软件包的存放目录</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#cd /usr/local/src/tar</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"># tar -zxvf memcache-3.0.8.tgz</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>挂载：让当前扩展获取</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-s