ze:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>②如果配合</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>CDN</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>使用，则会造成很大的经济效益，可以每年省下很多开支；</strong></span></span></p><h2><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>5、cdn</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">CDN</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">（</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Content Delivery Network</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">）内容分发网络，其侧重点是缓存。其能够长期缓存网站的静态文件。</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>优点：</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>①能缓存静态文件，节省带宽的开支；</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>②能够掩盖服务器端的真实</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size: