pan style=\"color:#0000FF;font-family:等线 Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>从服务器</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:等线 Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>是否同步成功</strong></span></span></h3><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql&gt;show slave status \\G;</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">如果看到</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">2</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">个</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">yes</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">表示成功。</span></span></p><h3><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>7、测试</strong></span></span></h3><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">可以在主数据库中新建一个数据库，然后在从数据库中</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">show</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">一下，如果显示有，则表示成功。</span></span></p><h2><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>5、LNMPA（</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt; background:#ff0000\"><strong>lamp</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>服务器）</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">架构：由于每个服务器软件有各自的优点，所以遵循“取其精华，去其糟粕”原则将每个服务器的特长发挥出来，组成了新的架构称之为</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">LNMPA</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">：由于</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">对静态页面的处理效率很好，所以</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在这个架构下专门负责处理静态；</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">：对于动态页面处理比较好，所以其负责处理动态页面。</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">开启</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">LAMP</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">架构服务器。开启之后获取</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">ip</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">地址，连接终端。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>①配置</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>nginx</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">安装</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">：去软件包的目录，执行脚本文件</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">install_nginx.sh</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在安装完成之后的界面：</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">location ~ .php$ {</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #</span></span> <span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">向后端服务器发起请求时添加指定的</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">header</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">头信息</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_set_header Host $http_host;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #</span></span> <span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">向后端服务器发送真实</span></span> <span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">IP</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #</span></span> <span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">让后端如</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">能直接通过变量获取真实</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">IP</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_pass&nbsp;&nbsp; http://127.0.0.1:8080;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">}</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"># nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">找不到文件时，转发请求给后端</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Apache</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">location @proxy {</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_set_header Host $http_host;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8080;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">}</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">将上述的配置放到</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx.conf</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">中：</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>②修改</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>apache</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>端口</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">修改</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的端口号为</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">8080</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"># vim /usr/local/http2/conf/httpd.conf</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>③设置</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>apache</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>站点根目录</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">由于当前的架构是服务于一个站点，因此需要将</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">2</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">个服务器软件的站点目录进行合并：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">选择</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的站点作为默认站点：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"># vim /usr/local/http2/conf/httpd.conf</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>④启动</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>apache</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>、</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>nginx</strong></span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>⑤测试访问</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的站点目录下创建</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">文件，测试结果：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#vim /usr/local/nginx/html/php54.php</span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">通过</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">windows</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">服务器进行浏览器测试：</span></span></p><p></p><p><br/></p>','29');
INSERT INTO `blog_article` VALUES('15','PHP高端技术之服务器架构','PHP高端技术之服务器架构','PHP高端技术之服务器架构','15','2017-07-14 15:35:32','uploads/20170714153528224.jpg','123','<h1><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:����;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>PHP高端技术之服务器架构（1）</strong></span></span></h1><h1><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>一、准备工作</strong></span></span></h1><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>1、linux系统安装</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Linux</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">常见的安装方式有</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">2</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">个：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">①真机安装</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">②虚拟机安装</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">（可以使用虚拟软件，</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">VM</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">、</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">VBox</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">）</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">注意事项：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">①在进行到网络配置的页面，不要去修改主机的名称，如果修改了后期会引起</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">启动不了；</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">②配置网络的时候默认开启“网卡自动连接”，以后虚拟机在开机之后会自动获取</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">ip</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">地址；</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">③在安装软件的时候，选择“现在自定义”、“开发”、“开发工具”，一定得把“开发工具”前面的复选框给勾选上；</span></span></p><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>2、上传所需软件</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">上传之前需要先获取虚拟机的</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">ip</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">地址：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">centos6.x</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">版本的系统中，获取</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">ip</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的命令是：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#ifconfig</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">centos7.x</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">版本的系统中，获取</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">ip</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的命令是：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#ip addr</strong></span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"91\" width=\"463\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">文件上传可以使用</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">filezilla</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">进行上传</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">上传保存目录必须是</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>/usr/local/src</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">目录。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"112\" width=\"692\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">将需要的文件：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">tar.tar.gz</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">上传到指定的目录：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"229\" width=\"385\"/></p><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>3、实用功能设置（建议）</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>①设置</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>vim</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>让其默认的显示号行。</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">设置方法：修改</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">vim</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的配置文件，</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">vim</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">每个用户自己的家目录中</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">存在一个配置文件（如果没有可以自己创建）文件名：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">.vimrc</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#cd ~</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#vim .vimrc</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"85\" width=\"311\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">保存退出</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>②设置清屏快捷键。</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">清屏命令：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#clear</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在开发的时候一般会把输入比较麻烦的命令做快捷键的设置。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">需要去配置快捷键的配置文件，存在于每个用户的家目录下，文件名叫做</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">.bashrc</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#vim .bashrc</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"199\" width=\"525\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在其中新增代码：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">alias cls=’clear’</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在设置完成别名操作之后需要当前用户重新去登录，才会生效。</span></span></p><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>4、系统克隆备份</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">很有必要性。防止系统在后期使用的时候崩溃。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">备份的时候需要关闭虚拟机中的操作系统。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">选择“管理”、“克隆”：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"228\" width=\"574\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"280\" width=\"589\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在进度条走完之后关闭对话框即可。</span></span></p><h1><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>二、</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>lamp</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>环境安装</strong></span></span></h1><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>1、安装前的说明</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>①查看新开主机的</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>ip</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>地址，使用远程终端连接操作</strong></span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"124\" width=\"533\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">后期的终端软件以putty为例。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"105\" width=\"466\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>②在</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>linux</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>下解压缩的命令</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>在</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>linux</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>下常见的压缩文件后缀有</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>tar.gz</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>、</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>bz2</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>解压</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>tar.gz</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>后缀的命令：</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#tar -zxvf</strong></span></span> <span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>需要解压的文件</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>解压</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>bz2</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>后缀的命令：</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#tar -jxvf</strong></span></span> <span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>需要解压的文件</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>③</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>shell</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>脚本</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">面试：你会不会写</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">shell</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">脚本？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>就是将</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>linux</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>下每一个单独的命令写到一个文件中去，这个文件我们称之为</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>shell</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>脚本</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Shell</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">脚本常用后缀有</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">.sh</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">。</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">shell</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">windows</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">下也存在应用，在</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">windows</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">下称之为批处理，常见后缀是</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">.bat</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">使用</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">shell</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">脚本的好处就是可以节省在安装过程中的时间。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"213\" width=\"482\"/></p><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>2、安装基础扩展库</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>脚本文件名：</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>install_base.sh</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在后期运行</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">和</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的时候需要一些基础软件的支持，例如使用</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">就会用到</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">GD</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">库，使用</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">就得使用</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">zlib</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">库，因此先得安装好对应的库和扩展。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">解压程序集合压缩包：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"105\" width=\"582\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"89\" width=\"686\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">安装需要执行脚本文件：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">install_base.sh</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"64\" width=\"685\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#./install_base.sh</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">安装完成之后看到的界面：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"107\" width=\"689\"/></p><h2><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:���� Light;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><strong>3、安装Apache</strong></span></span></h2><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>脚本文件名：</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>install_apache.sh</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">由于当前的操作系统已经安装好了</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">，所以需要先进行卸载操作。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"120\" width=\"683\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">删除命令：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#rpm -e</strong></span></span> <span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>需要删除的软件完整名称</strong></span></span> <span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>[--nodeps]</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#rpm -e httpd-2.2.15-39.el6.centos.i686 --nodeps</strong></span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"75\" width=\"690\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>①安装</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">需要执行安装的脚本文件：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">install_apache.sh</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#./install_apache.sh</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">安装完成之后看到的界面：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.li