e:10pt\"><strong>/usr/local/http2/conf/httpd.conf</strong></span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"85\" width=\"535\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>③关闭</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>/</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>卸载防火墙</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在学习环境下可以不用考虑防火墙，直接卸载防止影响后续的操作。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">先关闭防火墙的服务：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#service iptables stop</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">通过查询的命令查询防火墙软件的完整名称，然后再删除防火墙：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"107\" width=\"688\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>注意：如果防火墙服务没有在停止之后直接删除的，则需要在删除完成之后重新启动下</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>linux</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>操作系统。</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>④启动</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">Apache</span></span><span st