color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">语言编译器，和</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">gcc</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">类似），并且在安装</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的时候要求</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">cmake</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">最低版本是</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">2.8</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">。</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">同时还需要</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">ncurses-devel</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的支持。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"486\" width=\"692\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>脚本文件名：</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>install_mysql.sh</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>①安装</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">执行脚本文件</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">install_mysql.sh</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">完整的安装完成之后看到的界面：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"111\" width=\"692\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>②配置</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">生成配置文件：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#cp /usr/local/src/tar/mysql-5.5.17/support-files/my-medium.cnf /etc/my.cnf</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"66\" width=\"691\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">创建</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">用户以及用户组：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#useradd mysql</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"51\" width=\"691\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">使用命令</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#vim /etc/passwd</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">查看是否创建用户成功</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"58\" width=\"685\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">使用命令</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#vim /etc/group</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">查看是否创建用户组成功</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"63\" width=\"326\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">赋予</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">目录可执行权限：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#chmod +x /usr/local/mysql</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"38\" width=\"691\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">数据库初始化（创建测试数据库等），</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&amp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">表示在后台运行：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>/usr/local/mysql/scripts/mysql_install_db \\</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>--user=mysql \\</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>--basedir=/usr/local/mysql \\</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>--datadir=/usr/local/mysql/data &amp;</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">执行成功之后得看到</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">2</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">个“</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">OK</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">”</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"195\" width=\"684\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">如果卡屏则按下回车即可。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">把</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">安装文件</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">(</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">除了</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">data)</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的所有者都改为</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">root</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">，避免数据库恢复为出厂设置：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#chown -R root /usr/local/mysql</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#chown -R mysql /usr/local/mysql/data</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"89\" width=\"654\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">后台运行</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">服务（启动</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">）：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysqld_safe --user=mysql &amp;</strong></span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"114\" width=\"689\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">卡屏的时候按下回车</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">查看</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">是否有启动：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#ps -A|grep mysql&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"110\" width=\"686\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">如果看到有</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">2</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">个进程则说明</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">成功启动。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">测试数据库：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">#/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysql -u root</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">由于</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在安装之后默认</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">root</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">用户是没有密码的，所以不需要加上“</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">-p</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">”参数：</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"245\" width=\"686\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql&gt;show databases;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"288\" width=\"557\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>建设性操作，为了安全：</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">删除匿名用户：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql&gt;delete from mysql.user where User=&#39;&#39;;</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"74\" width=\"688\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">接上步，修改</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">密码</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">(</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">可不做此步，默认无密码</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">)</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql&gt;UPDATE mysql.user SET Password=password(&#39;123456&#39;) WHERE user=&#39;root&#39;;</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"64\" width=\"690\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql&gt;flush privileges;</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"70\" width=\"597\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>③测试</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">测试语句：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">mysql&gt;select version();</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"196\" width=\"630\"/></p><h1><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>三、</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>lnmp</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>环境安装</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></span></h1><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">在开发的时候常见的架构：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">①</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">LAMP</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">linux + apache + mysql/mariadb + php</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">②</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">LNMP</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">：</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">linux + nginx + mysql/maridb + php-fpm</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt; background:#ffff00\"><strong>面试题：</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt; background:#ffff00\"><strong>lamp</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt; background:#ffff00\"><strong>和</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt; background:#ffff00\"><strong>lnmp</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt; background:#ffff00\"><strong>有什么区别？</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">答：①底层架构上是不一样，在性能上</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apche</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">不如</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">效果好，</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">处理静态页效率非常高，</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">处理动态页面效果稍微好点；在安全性上，</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">要比</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">稍微好点；</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">②两个架构的</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">运行方式不一样。在</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">lamp</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">下，这个架构</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">都是以</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php5</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">模块的方式进行运行的（由于是</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">载入的</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">模块，所以每次修改</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">php</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">配置文件之后都需要去重启</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">apache</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">）；</span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>而在</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>lnmp</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>下其</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>php</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>的运行方式是使用的</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>fastCGI</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>模式，而这个模式是让</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>php</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>（特指</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>php-fpm</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>）以单独的进程去运行的，如果有</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>php</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>请求，则</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>nginx</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>将请求转发给</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>php-fpm</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>处理（有单独的端口，默认是</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>9000</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>），所以在</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>lnmp</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>下，如果</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>php</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>配置文件发生修改，则不需要重启</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"