tp://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"420\" width=\"692\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.lixiaohui.com/resources/org/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"graphic\" height=\"103\" width=\"684\"/></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">相关配置：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">location ~ .+\\.php($|/) {</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; set $script&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $uri;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; set $path_info&nbsp; &quot;/&quot;;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; if ($uri ~ &quot;^(.+\\.php)(/.+)&quot;) {</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; set $script&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $1;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; set $path_info&nbsp; $2;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#2E74B5;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span> <span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">fastcgi_index&nbsp; index.php?IF