\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">restart</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">的命令，重启方式有</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">2</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">种：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>方式</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>1</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>：</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>#/usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx -s reload</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">重新加载配置文件，并不是重启</span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">nginx</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>方式</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>2</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>：简单粗暴，先将</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>nginx</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#010101;font-family:宋体;font-size:12px\"